Simple "Advertisements Board" project created to test some technologies.
Used:
1. Tomcat 6.
2. Spring Security.
    - custom UserDetailsService(DaoUserDetailsService) which delegates user info requests to UserDAO.
    - isAnonymous function in SpringSecurityUtils.tld.
    - custom login page
3. JPA via Hibernate.
    - 2 simple entities. Collection of enums. Ether Criteria Api and JPQL.
    - Transactional integration tests for DAOs.
4. Stripes as MVC.
    - Custom ActionResolver, BaseActionBean
    - Implemented layout.jsp
    - JSP with JSTL, EL.